40521025@cf21@formal@none@1@S@The giant waves are more dangerous on flat shores than on steep ones.@@@@1@13@@oe@1-12-2014
40521026@cf21@formal@none@1@S@They usually range from 20 to 60 feet in height, but when they pour into a V-shaped inlet or harbor they may rise to mountainous proportions.@@@@1@26@@oe@1-12-2014
